        <abstract>
            <p>Had a pleasant week in London and is now enjoying Cambridge, where he is busy with work and social engagements.</p>
            <p>Writes with great enthusiasm of his prospective trip to "the Tropics" [Canary Islands]. Henslow will cram him in geology. He is working regularly at Spanish.</p>
        </abstract>
